{"tid":1022431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「付多少錢你自己決定」　慈善麵包店終究無法存活","createTime":"2019-02-15T04:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T05:54:11.000Z","uid":212399,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4d1cf75975a8c821b75c69c374c7ababb76b70ac","tid":1022431,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3897/d3897654.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3897%2Fd3897654.jpg&h=77ea5cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲慈善麵包店Panera Cares。（圖／達志影像／美聯社）<br />\n財經中心／綜合報導<br />\n美國一間名為「Panera Cares」的慈善麵包店，上門的顧客可以自己決定要付多少錢，雖然一度擴展到5間門市，但最終仍不敵營收壓力，門市陸續收攤，最後一間門市也將於15日關閉。<br />\n綜合外電報導，慈善麵包店「Panera Cares」是由美國連鎖麵包店「Panera Bread」創辦人Ron Shaich在2010年推出的，上門的顧客在消費時，可以自己決定要支付多少錢。在這樣的制度下，有能力的人可以多支付一點金額，生活困難的人則可以用較少今和享受到餐點，也可選擇以志工服務的方式換取餐點。<br />\n但現實情況是，2013年時，該公司曾透露，Panera Cares的營收與一般麵包店的營收相比僅有它們的7~8成，由於長期下來的經營壓力，原先有5間門市的Panera Cares，陸續收攤，就連最後一間位於波士頓的門市也將於今（15）日關門。<br />\nPanera Bread於2017被總部設在盧森堡的投資公司JAB控股公司收購（JAB Holding Co）。對於Panera Cares的關門，Panera Bread在聲明中表示，「很顯然，Panera Cares已經很難維持營運」。而對於因為Panera Cares門市關閉而失業的員工，Panera的發言人透露，公司將協助他們轉至其他關係企業任職。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190215/1378718.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190215%2F1378718.htm&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=509c9e21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190215/1378718.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c565b79414bc4f7395e43a664a67c24521b6ff39","tid":1022431,"uid":121580,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:30:55.000Z","msg":"7至8成都好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你試下支國"},{"pid":"04f21a1364f8ade577b9600aae6e7ecaa43d70f6","tid":1022431,"uid":35430,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:36:36.000Z","msg":"長期7 8成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633f607f0234370ba47f8d617112d5c01b5ec172","tid":1022431,"uid":55597,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c565b79414bc4f7395e43a664a67c24521b6ff39","tid":1022431,"uid":121580,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:30:55.000Z","msg":"7至8成都好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你試下支國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"支國都可能有人扮野比一大舊錢比一個包<br />\n香港應該全部比一蚊"},{"pid":"58f6e6f0e476f2d1b76b548ddf3f85212b2e7407","tid":1022431,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:41:20.000Z","msg":"好似幾高檔"},{"pid":"b701227c8ae06a9cb5cb58e5a9d1c7ba3336723a","tid":1022431,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"其實應該維到100先free出去梅花間竹咁"},{"pid":"e1957d386c73fe0c4d3f10157e14c51fb64e4808","tid":1022431,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"633f607f0234370ba47f8d617112d5c01b5ec172","tid":1022431,"uid":55597,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c565b79414bc4f7395e43a664a67c24521b6ff39","tid":1022431,"uid":121580,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:30:55.000Z","msg":"7至8成都好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你試下支國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"支國都可能有人扮野比一大舊錢比一個包<br />\n香港應該全部比一蚊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:44:35.000Z","msg":"支國以前好似有報攤試過，最後連檔口骨架都拆埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96ea2004bc1db3a93fb5434c8b8bdc3aac2946d","tid":1022431,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:45:44.000Z","msg":"人係自私, 貪心架"},{"pid":"b6f3c3627ab7fa771167adb72cb986525e3cb982